headline: Staples Canada and Allstate Protection Plans launch electronics trade-in program just in time for back-to-school savings
summary: Staples Canada, in partnership with Allstate Protection Plans, today announces the launch of Staples Trade-in by Allstate, a new program that allows Canadians to exchange their unwanted electronics for Staples e-gift cards. This initiative aims to support families and students by making it easy to save money and reduce e-waste ahead of the back-to-school season.
